## Key Data Sources (all free/public)

| Data | Source | Format |
|------|--------|--------|
| Offshore wind lease areas | [BOEM GIS Data](https://www.boem.gov/renewable-energy/mapping-and-data) | Shapefile/GeoJSON |
| Marine Protected Areas | [NOAA MPA Inventory](https://marineprotectedareas.noaa.gov/) | Shapefile |
| Shipping lanes / AIS | [MarineCadastre.gov](https://marinecadastre.gov/) | GeoJSON/CSV |
| Active Army Corps permits | [USACE Regulatory Permits](https://permits.usace.army.mil/) | Public records |
| Aquaculture permits | [NOAA Aquaculture](https://www.fisheries.noaa.gov/) | PDF/CSV |
| Subsea cables | [TeleGeography](https://www.submarinecablemap.com/) | GeoJSON |
| Bathymetry | [GEBCO](https://www.gebco.net/) | NetCDF/GeoTIFF |
